race.description: 2025 Peter Kittle Toyota Gawler Gold Cup F (G3)
race.comment: BOURNE MODEL (1) comes off a (30.69) win last time, scoring by half a length in a OPEN over 531m at this track. Has already won five times from this draw. Rates on top and should go close. WICKET (2) is a super consistent dog who rarely misses the frame, last start scoring at this track (30.69), making it two straight wins. Has a strong winning record here. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. KISAUNI (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 30.55 beating UNWORLDLY. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should be in this for a long way. SCHILLACI (3) has strong credentials over this journey.
